---
title: Hawaiian Halloumi (v) with Rice and Pineapple Salsa
description: Pineapple and cheese is an undisputed retro party classic. We've given it a modern twist with spiced halloumi and a zingy little salsa. You don't even need a foil-covered half grapefruit to enjoy this version!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spiced-halloumi-e7cd8c03-4f328092.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/spiced-halloumi-5968ed953bddb545b4237572-3aa7c7e8.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/hawaiian-halloumi-v-5968ed953bddb545b4237572
author: HelloFresh
time required: 30 minutes
cuisine: Mexican
